snippet.title: Thyranya - A tour in Thalassa
snippet.description:
A tour in the lively streets of Thalassa, enjoy! :)

Thyranya is a Free-to-play MMORPG coming in Q2-2026. 

The game is inspired on the famous dungeon crawler Diablo, MOBA's like League of Legends and MMORPG's like Tibia.

Thyranya aims to bring back the old-school feel, playability and graphics of classic MMORPGs, while adding modern features and combat mechanics of MOBAs and the darkness of dangerous and endless dungeons where survivors don't go back home empty handed.

And the ones who fail? You might be able to steal their coin and items from their corpses.

Thyranya has no mercy!

Ultimately, the goal of Thyranya is to make us all feel like we did one day when we used to play with your friends trying to complete quests, win a war or simply hang together for a catch up.

 Visit https://thyranya.com to learn more!
